data.description: Check our this fantastic investment opportunity! This 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom duplex is a landlord's dream, boasting long-term tenants that provide a steady income stream. This property offers the convenience of a 2 car garage with alley entrance, ensuring hassle-free parking for both tenants. The spacious backyard is a delightful retreat, perfect for relaxation and outdoor activities. With its cash-flowing potential and the security of established tenants, this duplex is an ideal addition to your real estate portfolio. Schedule a showing today and secure your piece of the real estate market!
